âIs Mr Fountain in?â he asked. âI have come about the advertisement.â

âOh, have you, sir?â she replied, making way for him to enter, and
showing him into a little sitting-room on the left of the passage.
âThe Captain is in bed; he is a great invalid, but he was expecting,
perhaps, some one would call, and he will be able to see you in a
