âOh, I only put it as a question; most people say they donât.â

âYes, but most people do.â

âI do,â said Lestrange.

He was silent for a moment.

âYou know my trouble so well that I wonât bother you going over it, but
there has come over me of late a feelingâit is like a waking dream.â

